r.s: Provides extra data structures and iterable/array functionality.
r.d: teds (Tentative Extra Data Structures) is a collection of data structures and iterable functionality
r.n: * Fix bugs in Teds\StrictHashSet/Teds\StrictHashMap iteration behavior. * Fix bug constructing balanced tree in Teds\StrictTreeSet/Teds\StrictTreeMap from array/unserializing, where certain sizes resulted in trees not maintaining the balancing invariant. * Fix bug when constructing Teds\IntVector from array when promoting type but not keeping reserved capacity. * Fix bugs in Teds\StrictSortedVectorSet::__construct
